reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Initial impression Good so Far
reviews.reviewText: Packaging is adequate. Looks great on the phone. Photo shows black Torras case on Midnight iPhone 13. Good camera and screen lip protection. Port and speaker cut outs on point. Works with screen protector. Grip is similar to Apple silicone case, not too slippery. Initially impressed with how good the quality feels on this case for the price! Hopefully it holds up well over time. Includes optional button colors to personalize your case. I chose yellow. :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 2, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I really love this green case so much. It's just as described, military-grade protection. And very good protection for my phone. The green color fits my temperament very well. So cool! Also, the translucent design of the back panel of this case can show off the shape of the phone even more and it looks very high-end.In fact, at that time I also searched for a lot of homes to compare. My favorite TORRAS is this phone case because a long time ago I heard of this brand. And I want to try it. I did not expect that the texture is really quite good. A little beyond my expectation. Very awesome!In the end, the after-sales service of TORRAS is also great. They provide a quality warranty, if you have any issues with your phone case during the use. Please contact them directly and they will give you a reasonable solution, which is great!I hope TORRAS will continue to work hard and make even better products!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Case is well made, no issues regarding fitment. Comes with 2 different button cover colors which I did not need to worry about messing with. The case is comfortable to hold. I got the RED one so I could see/find my phone easier after I lay it down.... Hi Vis doesn't hurt.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Overall really good case and it has protected my phone from money costly drops. Without a doubt the most appealing case ive ever had, though over time the color starts to stain and ive tried some ways to try to get the stains off but with no success.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars LOVE this phone case
reviews.reviewText: I have a very hard time finding cases that I find aesthetically pleasing and offer decent protection.This case has a very smooth, almost velvety silicone-type feel to it, yet the 3M sticker for my ring stand stays strongly put and it feels like you can keep a solid grip on it. Exactly what I needed.I saw two listings with the same case size specifications from Torras, but with a slightly different price and Alpine green was pictured in a different shade in each listing. Same name different shade. This particular listing appeared more army green and it is the one I went with. It is exactly the shade pictured. I can’t speak for the other listing though. It is thin, but feels like it offers decent protection. I added a glass screen and camera protector.Would definitely recommend this case.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect phone case
reviews.reviewText: I have bought this brand of case for my past 2 personal phones and past 2 work phones. I absolutely love them. The right amount of protection and still fits comfortably in your pocket. Fits phones perfectly as well, iPhones SE and 13 used on 2 of each model. Colored buttons are a nice touch and fit nice and snug. Had cases in the past with removable buttons that fell out of the case.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Better Than Expected
reviews.reviewText: For the price, this iPhone case is better than I expected. This iPhone 13 Pro case is fantastic and really suits my needs. The key features for me; It offers good protection around the corners and edges, the backside is raised providing needed protection around the camera, and it still maintains a slim profile. Most often my phone is in my hand, or my pocket. It has a comfortable grip, making it easier to hold the phone securely unlike some other cases that tend to have a slick feel, and the case is not bulky so it’s easy to hold on to and fits easily in my pocket. I’m sometimes careless with my phone, but with this case I can confidently pick it up without worrying about dropping it. If you’re looking for a good case at a reasonable price, I would recommend giving Torras phone cases a try.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A little slick for my hand, but an awesome case.
reviews.reviewText: I drop phones virtually constantly. This one was a little slick, but looks great, so I tried it out. Very sturdy, protects phone extremely well and looks very good.
